&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Locum Consultant in Paediatrics with a Special Interest in Diabetes&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This post is for a Locum Consultant General Paediatrician with a special interest in Diabetes. The post holder will have the majority of their duties based at Worcestershire Royal Hospital but will be expected to undertake outpatient clinics in a variety of settings around the county.They will also be expected to have an active involvement in the diabetes MDT. All inpatient Paediatric and Neonatal services are based at Worcestershire Royal Hospital.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The post includes general paediatric service weeks.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;For further information please contact Medical Resourcing viawah-tr.medicalresourcing@nhs.net&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
